metadata.title: HoloPark Founder's Token
metadata.name: HoloPark Founder's Token
metadata.description: The HoloPark is the ultimate virtual gaming arena and the world leader in fully immersive, haptic, virtual reality experiences. This limited edition HoloPark Founder's Token, 1 of only 40 ever to be minted, signifies the bearer is a lifetime member of the HoloPark Founder's Council; entitled to all the rights, privileges, and benefits defined by the HoloPark Founder's Charter.
